entries.quest_dock_d: Dock with the Rebel advanced recon freighter and transfer the reports to your vessel.
entries.quest_inspect_d: Once the vessel is disabled, inspect it and find any information that command can use.
entries.quest_location_d: A navigation waypoint of the Rebel Scout Shuttle will be supplied to you. Intercept and disable that vessel.
entries.split_quest_alert: Transfer the data that you captured from the communications vessel to an Imperial Intelligence shuttle. Stand by for nav location information.
entries.title: Endor System: Inspect the Rebel Scout Shuttle
entries.title_d: It would seem that the Rebels didn't expect you to survive their trap. There is one of their scout shuttles nearby that was coordinating the attack. Chances are good that they have the information we are after on that craft. Disable and inspect that vessel.
